所有非 distinct 聚合函数都是可以预聚合的
select count(distinct c1), sum(distinct c1), sum(c4),avg(c4),max(c1),min(c1) from lyqtest1 group by c2 order by 1,2;
+--------------------+------------------+---------+---------+---------+---------+
| count(distinct c1) | sum(distinct c1) | sum(c4) | avg(c4) | max(c1) | min(c1) |
+--------------------+------------------+---------+---------+---------+---------+
|                  1 |                1 |    10.5 |    10.5 |       1 |       1 |
|                  1 |                2 |    20.5 |    20.5 |       2 |       2 |
|                  1 |                3 |    30.5 |    30.5 |       3 |       3 |
+--------------------+------------------+---------+---------+---------+---------+
